p: SUBPOENA Territory of Washington County of Spokane}ss To Dolly Willows, Fannie Meller and Frank Webber In the name of the United States, you are hereby required to appear before the undersigned, on of the Justices of the Peace in and for the said County, on the 10 day of December 1885 at 11 o'clock A.M. at his office in Spokane Falls W.T. to give evidence in a certain cause then and there to be tried between The City of Spokane Falls Plaintiff and Frankie Sutsinger Defendant On the part of the plaintiff Given under my hand this 10 day of December 1885 J.J.L. Paul Justice of the Peace
